OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSouthern
OL,6,Fareas will stay dry with variable
OL,7,Fcloud and some clear spells. The north
OL,8,Fwill see a few light showers at times
OL,9,Falong with some clear intervals.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA lot of dry and bright
OL,12,Fweather with sunny interludes and
OL,13,Flight winds. A chance of one or two
OL,14,Flight showers, especially over
OL,15,Fnorthern counties in the morning.
OL,16,FLight winds.
